{"tid":447551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫學台] 我係唔係有 腸易激綜合症？","createTime":"2017-10-25T11:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T23:52:01.000Z","uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"690ddb607b315ea77e7687c7b49b7631fc73d3c2","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"腸胃一直唔好，朝早會痾氣痾黏液，<br />\n放工先會痾正常便便 (但事後左腰都係有D谷谷地頂住)<br />\n但夜晚臨訓又會想痾第3次，以前係黏液  依家多數正常一小舊<br />\n<br />\n睇醫生驗埋便便   都係話無事   <br />\n有個醫生話可能有少少IBS   另一個又話無撚事<br />\n<br />\n最後不了了之，到依家都5~6年了<br />\n可能唔夠訓有關 (一直1點幾訓，7點起身)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人有食開益生菌？有無幫助？我想買D來試下，求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625b67f90a9c476577ea3594b8dc45ab7e917f41","tid":447551,"uid":15344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbcff43ec1f96d35bbb76793cd78edf0d9a3fac","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"飲食時間正唔正常<br />\n平時食開咩<br />\n平時壓力大唔大<br />\n有冇咩病<br />\n有冇食緊咩藥<br />\n有冇食緊咩補健產品"},{"pid":"816933821058a8e57f3d26e1c553d8a4aa22568e","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"IBS照腸鏡仲實際啦"},{"pid":"b1388f012861f3616dc87d2b02cba3a0ab3567bf","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"Probiotics for Gastrointestinal Conditions: A Summary of the Evidence.<br />\n<br />\n...Probiotic effectiveness can be species-, dose-, and disease-specific, and the duration of therapy depends on the clinical indication...There is high-quality evidence that probiotics are effective for ..., irritable bowel syndrome...<br />\n<br />\nPMID: 28762696"},{"pid":"e8d2cc350e4871ce8f2709983742e28609e566f1","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲食時間正唔正常 <span style=\"color: green;\">正常，早午晚三餐，8點食晚飯，少吃零食，無宵夜</span><br />\n平時食開咩 <span style=\"color: green;\">白飯</span><br />\n平時壓力大唔大 <span style=\"color: green;\">不大，但1點訓 7點起，感到攰</span><br />\n有冇咩病 <span style=\"color: green;\">無，但認為自己有少少強迫症，洗手沖涼多步驟，check野有時check極都唔放心搞好耐，例如輸入資料會怕多左個space狂check</span><br />\n有冇食緊咩藥 <span style=\"color: green;\">無</span><br />\n有冇食緊咩補健產品 <span style=\"color: green;\">無</span> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"3dfd1a44ea5e06f9795c31643881dd67d32cf186","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880"},{"pid":"208869f46bad47a1399166882fd67ffbadbac8de","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到"},{"pid":"9f9ebffaec540e57d10c744f4600d3fc525c2327","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"As there is no specific biomarker or test to confirm or rule out a diagnosis of IBS, the Rome IV guidelines outline how the diagnosis of IBS requires a thoughtful approach, limited diagnostic tests, and careful follow-up.4 The <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">presence of recurrent abdominal pain in association with abnormal bowel habits are the defining features of IBS</span></strong> (Table 1).<br />\n<br />\nRecurrent abdominal <strong>pain, on average, at least one day per &emsp;week in the last three months</strong>, <strong>associated with&thinsp;&ge;&thinsp;2</strong> of &emsp;the following criteria:<br />\n&emsp;1. Related to defecation.<br />\n&emsp;2. Associated with a change in frequency of stool.<br />\n&emsp;3. Associated with a change in form (appearance) of stool."},{"pid":"477a1b1a0a10a8ba54841a995e3138e931a08ca8","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png&h=274428c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09ae23de2bbf4e6e73d8c2be9a47d5c963575297","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"google PMC5625880 自己睇仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c490341d115e00a69c7edaae7fafd8847549fb20","tid":447551,"uid":131312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"認真，飲益力多，有用"},{"pid":"74faa25f0c0f99cff6c361c4e06bdbff75ee87d4","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png&h=274428c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n- <strong>不嬲無肚痛</strong>，但係︰<br />\n    - 右胸下方肋骨處 (右Lin往下8cm再向右5cm，肋骨之間) 時不時有短促痛楚，比較subtle既痛，唔係針拮，較似胃痛個種&quot;拿拿地&quot;既，每次3~5秒，係漸起又漸落而去。<br />\n    - 左腰近背，有時會有頂住頂住既感覺。通常放工痾屎時特別覺，而痾完都重有呢個感覺。沖完個涼就會慢慢唔覺。"},{"pid":"3ba3ebec6e522ae1c0bac03d62e37a99965b83f0","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，飲益力多，有用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個禮拜有飲，但不覺得有咩強大功效"},{"pid":"c8645796338dca204839dc8e6e234431d2e33b4b","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png&h=274428c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n- <strong>不嬲無肚痛</strong>，但係︰<br />\n    - 右胸下方肋骨處 (右Lin往下8cm再向右5cm，肋骨之間) 時不時有短促痛楚，比較subtle既痛，唔係針拮，較似胃痛個種&quot;拿拿地&quot;既，每次3~5秒，係漸起又漸落而去。<br />\n    - 左腰近背，有時會有頂住頂住既感覺。通常放工痾屎時特別覺，而痾完都重有呢個感覺。沖完個涼就會慢慢唔覺。</blockquote><br />\n驗血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇biomedical results 一切都係9估"},{"pid":"560f24b248d544ccb9eb99b909d18af1cb839ed8","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"依家即刻去飲支益力多先 (雖然覺得無效)"},{"pid":"19438566960a19b0409b3425b84c7468a4fa5247","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png&h=274428c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n- <strong>不嬲無肚痛</strong>，但係︰<br />\n    - 右胸下方肋骨處 (右Lin往下8cm再向右5cm，肋骨之間) 時不時有短促痛楚，比較subtle既痛，唔係針拮，較似胃痛個種&quot;拿拿地&quot;既，每次3~5秒，係漸起又漸落而去。<br />\n    - 左腰近背，有時會有頂住頂住既感覺。通常放工痾屎時特別覺，而痾完都重有呢個感覺。沖完個涼就會慢慢唔覺。</blockquote><br />\n驗血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇biomedical results 一切都係9估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前驗屎 (樽仔sample + 便血 tests)<br />\n再抽血<br />\n<br />\nBOTH無野<br />\n問醫生︰喂我係咪IBS呀？<br />\n佢答︰唔係<br />\n<br />\n真係吹脹    病情繼續"},{"pid":"842907201d903d92e2166056aa8733ae11a84492","tid":447551,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"利申︰睇政府街症"},{"pid":"719719d512c3af27d60d182587e21a46ee98da79","tid":447551,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au/pmc/articles/PMC5625880/bin/10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ncbi-nlm-nih-gov.ezproxy1.library.usyd.edu.au%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5625880%2Fbin%2F10.1177_2050640617731968-fig1.jpg&h=f47c554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimplified algorithm for irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) diagnosis.<br />\n<br />\nPMC5625880</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks, 但我無UniKey account睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F200232_39e0571da25b1f048e893e7fd03c43d8.png&h=274428c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquot