te><blockquote>就咁睇好正常喎老友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得我係普通腸胃問題？</blockquote><br />\n似係太擔心喎<br />\n<br />\nPMID: 24705634 <br />\n(雖然呢份講緊anxiety v.s. IBS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"}]}